room_title: Escape room "Alien Invasion" by Maine Escape Games in South Portland
room_address: 125 John Roberts Rd, Suite 8 South Portland, ME 04106
room_description: A UFO has crashed into Maine Escape Games, and now it's leaking deadly radiation. You and your team have one hour to find a way into the spaceship, figure out how to restore its power, and stop the leak before you succumb to the lethal emission.
